 } } \right| = 1(24 - 10) + 1(10 - 12)$$<br><br>$$ = 14 - 2 = 12 \ne 0$$<br><br>Here, D $$ \ne $$ 0 $$ \Rightarrow $$ unique solution for any b<sub>1</sub>, b<sub>2</sub>, b<sub>3</sub>.<br><br>(b) $$D = \left| {\matrix{
   1 &amp; 1 &amp; 3  \cr 
