 } } \right|$$<br><br>$$ = 1( - 6 + 6) - 1( - 15 + 12) + 3( - 5 + 4) = 0$$<br><br>For at least one solution<br><br>$${D_1} = {D_2} = {D_3} = 0$$<br><br>Now, $${D_1} = \left| {\matrix{
